nodes.text: The Devaronian Kivas owned a depot in the town of Tikaroo, which was located on the planet Devaron. It was described by Luke Skywalker as "ramshackle," and was built out of a number of materials, including wood, stone, prefab plastic, and shipping containers. While in Tikaroo, Skywalker left his BTL Y-wing starfighter in the depot for repairs.
